EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 2000Z DAILY
   01 AND 02 APR WITHIN 60 MILES OF
   57-02.0N 009-07.4W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON
   VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 022100Z APR.
